  "id": 2907,
  "name": "Esca zuccherosa",
  "desc": "<p>The bait is based on rose dew and has been mixed with sun-dried Harra Fruit powder. It has a spicy taste and a sweet aftertaste, just like the life of a fisherman. The harvest after going through all the weather-beaten days and roaring waves is particularly gratifying.</p><p></p><p>Suitable for: Angler and Axe Marlin.</p>",
